Ronald Reagan met Mikhail Gorbachev at a peace summit in Geneva in 1985 . 
  He asked the Soviet leader for his support in the event of an alien invasion . 
  The former US President was said to be obsessed with science fiction films like Close Encounters and The Day the Earth Stood Still . 
  Reagan repeated the warning to a group of students at the peace summit . 
  His advisers were said to have removed any mention of aliens from his speeches . 
  Dr David Clarke said Reagan appeared to believe in aliens . 
 